":20,"t":"The Actions page helps you act on insights generated by ProductHelp AI.","s":"Taking Actions","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/actions","h":"","p":19},{"i":22,"t":"Create tasks based on user issues Assign actions to team members Track progress of improvements Close issues once resolved","s":"What you can do here","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/actions","h":"#what-you-can-do-here","p":19},{"i":24,"t":"Identify a recurring issue from the dashboard Create an action item Assign it to the relevant team Track resolution status This ensures that insights are not just observed, but acted upon.","s":"Example workflow","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/actions","h":"#example-workflow","p":19},{"i":26,"t":"The dashboard gives you a complete view of how users interact with your product.","s":"Dashboard Overview","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/dashboard","h":"","p":25},{"i":29,"t":"Understand what users are searching for and where they are struggling.","s":"Search Insights","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/dashboard","h":"#search-insights","p":25},{"i":31,"t":"View the most common problems users are facing.","s":"Top Issues","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/dashboard","h":"#top-issues","p":25},{"i":33,"t":"Track how support tickets are increasing or decreasing over time.","s":"Ticket Trends","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/dashboard","h":"#ticket-trends","p":25},{"i":35,"t":"AI-generated suggestions to improve product experience and reduce friction. Use the dashboard regularly to monitor trends and identify areas of improvement.","s":"Recommendations","u":"/my-docs-site/docs/user-guide/dashboard","h":"#recommendations","p":25},{"i":38,"t":"ProductHelp AI is an AI-powered insights platform that helps teams understand user behavior, identify product pain points, and reduce support tickets. It combines intelligent search, usage insights, and contextual recommendations to help teams take faster and more informed decisions.","s":"What is ProductHelp AI?","